{
  "stem": "18575.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 451.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the fighting was going on in a small way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Groups such as the brushworks, a factory that make brushes and others, had barricaded themself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were fighting with the-- with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, you're fighting with a fully-equipped army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The air force, the-- the Luftwaffe, was bombing the ghetto with incendiary bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "With the dive bomb, it's very precise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So nothing on the Aryan sides was hit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Germans were, with flame throwers, burning house after house and blowing it up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "People-- like, me were hidden in the bunkers, which were cellars, blocked off cellars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were finding it with a listening device.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they had sensitive listening devices that they were walking and listening for voices of movement.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were in one of the buildings, I and my-- by the way, in one of the trips that I had taken with a fellow to deliver some clothing to the group, when I returned, I found my-- my wife-- my mother was shot, killed.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We, the three of us, we went from one bunker-- and it was destroyed-- to another.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In one of the bunkers, we was there where the German have put to fire above.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they threw grenades.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the ceiling collapsed on us with the fire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I got burned.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I got third-degree burn on my hand, left hand, and my right foot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My skin peeled off like a glove.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was in horrible pain, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We ran out from there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "My friends carried me, actually, to another bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I just had a-- a shirt, old shirt that I wrapped around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I had-- they started infection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was a couple days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Got green.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I got fever.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
